sentence: The latest tally of analyst opinions from the major brokerage houses shows that among the 30 stocks making up the Dow Jones Industrial Average, Procter & Gamble Company (PG) is the #14 analyst pick.
Procter & Gamble Company also comes in above the median of analyst picks among the broader S&P 500 index components, claiming the #186 spot out of 500.
Looking at the stock price movement year to date, Procter & Gamble Company (PG) is lower by about 1.8%.
